{"data":[{"date":"07:13 19/07","title":"Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba sau qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Fred v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot, ngay sau khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chia-tay-johnstone-172-190315.html\" target=\"_blank\">chia tay \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Sam Johnstones</span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 35 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1ee9 ba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero trong khung g\u1ed7 Old Trafford. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong khung g\u1ed7 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Perreira.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh ra m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mua Lee Grant b\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Joel Perreira ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai n\u0103m tr\u1eddi \u1edf c\u00e1i tu\u1ed5i 22 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 Lee, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea3 Championship c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Joel ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng Joel \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai</span><br>\r\nManchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1403","checkdouble":"191560"},{"date":"07:37 19/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Florentino Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Cristiano Ronaldo.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Hazard thay Ronaldo?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau khi chia tay si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafm vai ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 g\u1ea7n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u00e3 qua, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh Los Blancos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c b\u1ea1o chi h\u01a1n sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c bom t\u1ea5n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, cam \u0111oan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Alvaro Odriozola, t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro mua t\u1eeb Valencia v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3, lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp theo.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u1ea5t cho hay, Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea</span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3\u201d s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Julen Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1402","checkdouble":"191561"},{"date":"08:40 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 vinh danh nh\u1eefng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c Eden Hazard hay G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng ni\u1ec1m vui kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Chelsea khi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Hazard tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span>, Courtois c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng r\u1eb1ng\u2026 Hazard \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u, anh theo \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy\u1ec7t chi \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c th\u00e0nh London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho Maurizio Sarri khi c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u1ea5m ch\u1ed7 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00e2n HLV 59 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh m\u1ea5t \u0111i hai ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ngay khi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu HLV h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi n\u00f3, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u00f3 trong tay, v\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea5m Hazard n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i h\u1ecfi han Hazard trong l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 4-5 ng\u00e0y trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho Chelsea.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1401","checkdouble":"191562"},{"date":"08:49 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alvaro Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui. Anh c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"http://bongdaplus.vn/alvaro-odriozola-tan-binh-cua-real-madrid-la-ai-2218061807.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2n binh Odriozola</span> m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real h\u00f4m qua sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Sociedad n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 35 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, Odriozola c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Odriozola v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 thay v\u00ec hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Sergi Roberto v\u00e0 Hector Bellerin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV\u00a0Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m Odriozola c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 HLV Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u1ea1i Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u00e1ng nay. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u cao. V\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Lopetegui th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Lopetegui kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c khi Zidane r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng ra \u0111i. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real thay m\u00e1u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo-180-191561.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1400","checkdouble":"191566"},{"date":"08:47 19/07","title":"Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/26/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1eafp c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Alisson, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Liverpool chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Naby Keita, Fabinho v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Liverpool, ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. Nh\u00ecn chung, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 The Kop m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Man City cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eeb Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu 3 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jurgen Klopp l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00ec nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian qua d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi West Ham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u00fap Klopp \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 100% nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t\u201d, Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp\" title=\"Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLu\u00f4n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng theo c\u1ea3 hai h\u01b0\u1edbng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Liverpool ch\u1ec9 \u0111i theo m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n binh, s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng nhau, b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Premier League sau Man City, Man United v\u00e0 Tottenham. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua Real Madrid 3-1 b\u1edfi 2 sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-dung-tien-de-bep-liverpool-vu-alisson-172-191489.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Liverpool v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1399","checkdouble":"191567"},{"date":"23:33 18/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/3/4/da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t khi m\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Inte Milan quy\u1ebft gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi\u00a0ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Inter \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 khi anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi 44% t\u1ed5ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 Nerazzui c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Icardi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba chia tay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Ronaldo. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u2018ve v\u00e3n\u2019 c\u1ee7a Real, CLB Inter Milan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u2018tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u2019 Icardi. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Gazzetta dello Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd s\u1edbm g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 7,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 5,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i Serie A. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Icardi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus - Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Inter cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Inter t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7: Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale</span><br>\r\nReal ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale, Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic cho M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1398","checkdouble":"191546"},{"date":"04:25 19/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo Goal, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Jorginho</span> khi\u1ebfn HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n The Blues \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Cuc-nong-Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-36-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Gary Cahill kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i d\u00f9 \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. David Luiz th\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ngo\u00e0i ra m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Conte khi\u1ebfn anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Chelsea c\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDavid Luiz \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge, HLV Sarri s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Gary Cahill. C\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Luiz v\u00e0 Cahill \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Daniele Rugani.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Empoli t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013 \u0111\u1ebfn 2015, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Rugani. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Juventus nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Giorgio Chiellini, Medhi Benatia v\u00e0 Andrea Barzagli, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 26 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo Goal, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m th\u1ee9 3 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 Fali Ramadani \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fabio Paratici c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daniele Rugani. Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u1edf Milan di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, theo \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 7.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Daniele Rugani, anh s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 4,5 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus v\u1eeba b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Sau Rugani, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gonzalo Higuain c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1397","checkdouble":"191548"},{"date":"04:38 19/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Pogba ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, anh duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/day-ly-do-cho-thay-pogba-moi-la-thu-linh-dich-thuc-cua-tuyen-phap-421-191492.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p</span>, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft Pogba \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i V\u0110TG, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Hugo Lloris l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 30 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Pogba\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Pogba l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Pogba h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho phat bieu ve Pogba\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mourinho-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00edch t\u01b0\u1edbng Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau khi \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u1edf Nga, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Pogba m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPogba ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn NHM ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi MU s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1396","checkdouble":"191549"},{"date":"04:53 19/07","title":"MU mu\u1ed1n \"\u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m\" Bayern Munich","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang The Independent \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago v\u00e0 Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9ng 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean \u0111a n\u0103ng Dalot v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Fred.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong MU muon co Lewandowski va Thiago\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang The Independent \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho nh\u1eafm Thiago nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Carrick, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Barca v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lukaku \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm Lewandowski nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i. M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Khong de de MU co Lewandowski va Thiago\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/de.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 46 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Bayern ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, M.U c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Thiago \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Real trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Lewandowski trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Bayern Munich ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Thiago v\u00e0 110 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Lewandowski.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thiago v\u00e0 Lewandowski, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marko Arnautovic c\u1ee7a West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1395","checkdouble":"191550"},{"date":"05:18 19/07","title":"Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tru-cot.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chamberlain-chan-thuong-nghiem-trong-172-185032.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span>. C\u1ef1u sao Arsenal ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 18 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Kolarov.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tru-cot.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chamberlain ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Chamberlain g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 Chamberlain s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Chamberlain g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Chamberlain\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Chamberlain \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chamberlain chan thuong va se phai nghi thi dau dai han\" title=\"Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/klopp-van-mong-cho-dieu-ky-dieu-voi-chamberlain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Chamberlain \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn Anfield v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChamberlain \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn, \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1394","checkdouble":"191551"},{"date":"05:37 19/07","title":"Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Paul Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mourinho-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Pogba ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, anh duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/day-ly-do-cho-thay-pogba-moi-la-thu-linh-dich-thuc-cua-tuyen-phap-421-191492.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p</span>, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft Pogba \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i V\u0110TG, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Hugo Lloris l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 30 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Pogba\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Pogba l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Pogba h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho phat bieu ve Pogba\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/mourinho-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00edch t\u01b0\u1edbng Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau khi \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u1edf Nga, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Pogba m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPogba ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn NHM ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi MU s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1393","checkdouble":"191552"},{"date":"06:19 19/07","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Jorginho </span>t\u1eeb Napoli, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsa mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Napoli v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Jorginho v\u00e0 Kante, HLV Sarri \u0111ang \u0111i t\u00ecm th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 14 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 44 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng Pjanic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u1edf Chelsea, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n Chelsea l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Miralem Pjanic \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" title=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/23/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pjanic l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPjanic v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fali Ramadani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0103n t\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Milan v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia v\u1ec1 Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Pjanic mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 The Blues d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Ngo\u00e0i Pjanic, Chelsea c\u00f2n quan t\u00e2m Daniele Rugani v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain c\u0169ng c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1392","checkdouble":"191553"},{"date":"06:02 19/07","title":"Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/2/mourinho-quyet-tam-chan-duong-roi-old-trafford-cua-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester \u2013 V\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Martial r\u1eddi Old Trafford</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 khi Alexis Sanchez xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Old Trafford c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/2/mourinho-quyet-tam-chan-duong-roi-old-trafford-cua-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Martial r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Martial ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Philippe Lamboley c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Martial s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Martial</span>, Juventus, PSG, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester \u2013 V\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cLukaku v\u00e0 Rashford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng ngh\u1ec9 sau th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Martial l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Martial \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 chia l\u1eeda v\u1edbi Lukaku, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Sanchez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, tuy nhi\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs MU Sanchez di bong\" title=\"Chelsea vs MU Sanchez di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Goc-nhin-Mourinho-co-xung-dang-duoc-MU-tiep-tuc-tin-tuong-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o Sanchez s\u1ebd sang M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, Sanchez b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t \u00e1n treo k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 16 th\u00e1ng, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian th\u1ee5 \u00e1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLu\u1eadt M\u1ef9 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111ang th\u1ee5 \u00e1n \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n tr\u1eeb, Sanchez n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn anh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sanchez, HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o Sanchez s\u1ebd t\u1edbi M\u1ef9, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng M.U th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho t\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nhanh ch\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1391","checkdouble":"191554"},{"date":"06:10 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (19/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_ur