 display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 19/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1907 MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1907 MU chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-1907-MU-chi-130-trieu-bang-cho-2-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Chamberlain</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chamberlain ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t khi m\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Unai Emery v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Godin\" title=\"trung ve Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Godin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot Malcom c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, Everton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom c\u1ee7a Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial Mourinho\" title=\"Martial Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/2/mourinho-quyet-tam-chan-duong-roi-old-trafford-cua-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester &ndash; V\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Martial \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Pjanic&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang-172-191553.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-kich-no-bom-tan-70-trieu-bang-172-191553.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea mua Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1389","checkdouble":"191558"}]}